(49,'Tajikistan’s leading micro lending institution, Imon International (Imon), will continue providing financial services to more than 100,000 micro businesses and individual borrowers across the country thanks to an equity investment from Imon’s international shareholders, according to the Bank for Reconstruction and Development (EBRD) Resident Office in Dushanbe.

